# TaskFlow - Modern Task Management Tool

![TaskFlow Demo](https://via.placeholder.com/800x400.png?text=TaskFlow+Demo+GIF)

A real-time collaborative task management application inspired by Trello. Built with React, Node.js, and Socket.io.

##  Features

### Core Features
-  **User Authentication** - JWT-based auth with Google OAuth
-  **Board Management** - Create, delete, customize boards
-  **Lists & Cards** - Drag-and-drop functionality
-  **Real-time Updates** - See changes instantly across clients
-  **Collaboration** - Invite members, assign tasks
-  **Card Details** - Labels, due dates, checklists, attachments
-  **Comments & Activity** - @mentions, real-time comments

### Advanced Features
-  **Custom Backgrounds** - Unsplash integration
-  **Notifications** - In-app and email
-  **Board Analytics** - Activity insights
-  **Full-text Search** - Find cards quickly
-  **Responsive Design** - Works on all devices

##  Tech Stack

### Frontend
- React 18 with TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- dnd-kit for drag-and-drop
- Zustand for state management
- Socket.io-client for real-time
- React Router v6
- Vite as build tool

### Backend
- Node.js with Express
- MongoDB with Mongoose
- Socket.io for WebSockets
- JWT for authentication
- Multer for file uploads
- Jest for testing

### DevOps
- Docker & Docker Compose
- GitHub Actions for CI/CD
- Nginx as reverse proxy
- PM2 for process management

##  Installation

### Prerequisites
- Node.js 18+
- MongoDB 6+
- npm or yarn

### Clone the repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/task-management-tool.git
cd task-management-tool
